- First time checkout
> git clone https://jstrube@bitbucket.org/jstrube/linearcolliderdetectorrnd.git

- How to compile the latex document (works on linux and Mac OS X):
> ./compileLatex

- How to update your repository to pull in the latest changes from the server:
> git pull

- How to add a new file to the version control system:
> git add <filename>
> git commit -m "added a file with important content"
> git push origin master

- How to commit the changes to a file that already existed before:
> git commit -am "Changed the Authorlist" <filename>
> git push origin master

- How to check which files are under version control:
> git status

- How to read the commit messages:
> git log
